data.text:
TOKYO, Japan - American actor producer Clint Eastwood (L) shakes hands with Tokyo Governor Shintaro Ishihara at the governor's office on April 6. Eastwood asked Ishihara for his cooperation in shooting a film featuring Tokyo's Io Island during the Pacific War. (Kyodo)
